ic Members and their execution control flow</li><li style=\"margin-left: 4rem; list-style-type: decimal;\">Final Variables and their rules</li><li style=\"margin-left: 4rem; list-style-type: decimal;\">Classes and Types of classes</li><li style=\"margin-left: 4rem; list-style-type: decimal;\">OOPS- Fundamentals, Models, Relations and Principles</li><li style=\"margin-left: 4rem; list-style-type: decimal;\">Coupling and Cohesion (MVC and LCRP Architectures)</li><li style=\"margin-left: 4rem; list-style-type: decimal;\">Types of objects &amp; Garbage Collection</li><li style=\"margin-left: 4rem; list-style-type: decimal;\">Arrays and Var-arg types</li><li style=\"margin-left: 4rem; list-style-type: decimal;\">Enum and Annotation</li><li style=\"margin-left: 4rem; list-style-type: decimal;\">Design Patterns</li></ol><h3 style=\"font-size: 21px; font-family: \" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(34,=\"\" 34,=\"\" 34);=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 600;=\"\" margin-bottom:=\"\" 1.6rem;=\"\" line-height:=\"\" 21px;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" rgba(255,=\"\" 255,=\"\" 0.8);\"=\"\"><span id=\"Java_API_and_Project\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Java API and Project</span></h3><ol style=\"font-size: 12px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 2.6rem; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\"><li style=\"margin-left: 4rem; list-style-type: decimal;\">API and API Documentation</li><li style=\"margin-left: 4rem; list-style-type: decimal;\">Fundamental Classes – Object, Class, System, Runtime</li><li style=\"margin-left: 4rem; list-style-type: decimal;\">String Handling</li><li style=\"margin-left: 4rem; list-style-type: decimal;\">Exception Handling and Assertions</li><li style=\"margin-left: 4rem; list-style-type: decimal;\">Multithreading with JVM Architecture</li><li style=\"margin-left: 4rem; list-style-type: decimal;\">IO Streams (File IO)</li><li style=\"margin-left: 4rem; 